data.description: Relax in coastal comfort in this two story home located in Lamar . Its Just minutes from Goose Island State Park where you can enjoy fishing on the lighted pier, hiking the nature trails. Also enjoy St Charles Bay just down the street where you can fish off the shore or launch you boat/kayaks. Dont forget just a golf cart ride down the street to enjoy watching the whooping cranes and pelicans and all the deer. This adorable home has three bedrooms and two full baths upstairs and two living spaces and half bath downstairs.Also hasa bonus room downstairs that could be a fourth bedroom. Electricity is supplied by solar panels.The She Shed in the backyard has a window unit and multiple 110 plugs and the Man Cave has plenty of room for all his toys and a nice deck with TV and BBQ grill to sit outside under all the live oaks and enjoy the coastal life. Home sits on two big Lots and plenty of room to park your boat and RV.
